212
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:52,500
Ya está.

213
00:17:54,000 --> 00:17:56,000
Ooh, ahora si que reboso de placer.

214
00:17:57,700 --> 00:18:00,700
Oye, vas a comerte el resto
